        <h1>Paragraph</h1>
        <hr style="width:100%;">
        <p>
            A paragraph is a group of related sentences that support one main idea. In general, paragraphs consist of three parts: the topic sentence, body sentences, and the concluding or the bridge sentence to the next paragraph or section of the paper.
        </p>
    </body>
